{"tid":1161746,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖) 日本媒體報導:  視死如歸的中國女兵","createTime":"2019-05-19T11:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:55:55.000Z","uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7da6a71a9bf5b849e3d6e9f1eb49fd9beec36849","tid":1161746,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:47:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/CantoneseMuseum/photos/a.405413536135531/2450572228286308/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCantoneseMuseum%2Fphotos%2Fa.405413536135531%2F2450572228286308%2F&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPXejezXkYyU2Z26LisGJHUw%3D&h=603e8f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/CantoneseMuseum/photos/a.405413536135531/2450572228286308/</a><br />\n<br />\n廣東話資料館 Cantonese Museum<br />\n1 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>《支那事變畫報》1938年入面嘅〔成本華〕照片！</strong><br />\n<br />\n呢本畫報係日本昭和13年〔1938年5月20日〕，由日本朝日新聞社出版發行嘅。喺畫報入面，成本華企喺一間木屋前面，畀四件日本兵圍住，佢英勇不屈，視死如歸，最後畀日本軍殘酷殺害。<strong>犧牲嘅時候，成本華只有24歲。</strong><br />\n<br />\n相入面嘅日文註釋好短：「和縣城門上捉到嘅唯一敵軍士兵、女俘虜成本華，佢嘅腰帶上帶有『中國女童子軍』字樣，<strong>呢名抗日頑固分子冇吐露絲毫軍事機密</strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n佔領大西洋。廣東話資料館<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/ROzEWRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FROzEWRJ.jpg&h=514d3daf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9dbf1beb6c55ac14b8ade3d85fdc164171be369","tid":1161746,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e0229c62ad390fbe486e35340a5bb64bd3a59c","tid":1161746,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5897edb07647e69d78fcef2767a43efcfc664011","tid":1161746,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac